MSV
The Russian Motor Rifle Troops or MSV ( Моторизо́ванные стрелко́вые войска, МСВ ) is one of the two main forces of Russian Federation Ground forces.


RVA
The Russian Rocket Troops and Artillery or RVA ( Моторизо́ванные стрелко́вые войска, РВА ) is one of the branches of Russian Federation Armed Forces.


TV
The Russian Tank Troops or TV ( Моторизо́ванные стрелко́вые войска, TВ ) is one of the two main forces of Russian Federation Ground forces.


VDV
The Russian Airborne Troops or VDV ( Воздушно-десантные войска, ВДВ ) is the elite military branch of the Russian Federation Armed forces responsible for airborne assaults, deploying from the Russian's Air Force planes to deliver combined-arms task forces where needed.


VMF
The Russian Naval Force or VMF ( Военно-морской Флот Российской Федерации, ВМФ ) is one of the branches of Russian Federation Armed forces.


VPVO
The Russian Air Defense Troops or VPVO ( Противовоздушная оборона, ПВО ) is the military branch of the Russian Federation Armed forces responsible for air defense.


VV
The Russian Internal Troops or VV ( Внутренние войска Министерства внутренних дел, ВВ ) is a paramilitary force of the Ministry for Internal Affairs. In wartime the Internal forces fall under the Armed Forces military command to fulfill local defense missions and rear area security.


VVS
The Russian Air Force or VVS ( Военно-воздушные cилы , ВВC ) is the military branch of the Russian Federation Armed forces responsible for aerial warfare.